txt.en: 'You think you have what it takes to be a flet-runner, [placeholder]? I do not know that you are familiar enough with Caras Galadhon or have the fleetness that it requires!\n\n'Prove to me that you do by making your way to the flet-runner on the larger of the high flets of Telain Neduil and with time to spare!'
'You made it here in time, [placeholder]! I did not think it would be so!'
'Why do you delay? Think you that the time is more than sufficient? If you are not correct, you will never make it in time to the flet-runner on the large high flet belonging to Telain Neduil.'
